About the Project
uh uh uh! wrong place. not here

Ok here!

Some drugs contain certain ingredients that trigger certain side effects and or ailments. 
Most persons do know what they are allergic to or what their bodies cannot take but what 
they do not know is if the next drug has it or not.

e-PillBox is meant to provide as much information as possible in the most accurate method 
available to ensure that each patient is aware of what they consume.

Available in: Web Version | Mobile Version | Android App

